p__1_5');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >5</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Genesis 49:21.</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_6\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_6');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >6</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">The 9th of Tebeth being the anniversary of his death.</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_7\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_7');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >7</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Ezekiel.</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_8\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_8');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >8</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Ezekiel 24:2.</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_9\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_9');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >9</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Teḅeth is the tenth month of the ecclesiastical year.</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_10\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_10');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >10</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Ezekiel 33:21 b, with 